column5: Hey Guys and Gals,  Going to spend the day on Lake of Bays tomorrow. I was wondering if anyone knew of a restaurant in walking distance on the water. We would like to park the boat and check out a local marina for shopping and maybe fries and a burger. Going to be launching out of Baysville.  Thanks in Advance

Hi Henry, Dorset has a restaurant on the water where you can pull up your boat and have some food. There is also some shops in the town.  I believe Baysville also has a restaurant on the water, however, I have never been so can say for certain.  Hope that helps
Dorset is your best bet for food.  I live in Baysville anything here is away from the water not a far walk but not on water.  good luck on Sunday.    Ian
